<indexterm><primary>checkI2C</primary><secondary>Tools method</secondary></indexterm>
<indexterm><primary>Tools method</primary><secondary>checkI2C</secondary></indexterm>
<para><computeroutput>int RDA5807::checkI2C (uint8_t * addressArray)</computeroutput></para><para>

<para>Check the I2C bus address. </para>
</para>

<para>
                <formalpara>
                    <title>
Parameters</title>
                    <para>
                    <table frame="all">
                        <tgroup cols="2" align="left" colsep="1" rowsep="1">
                        <colspec colwidth="1*"/>
                        <colspec colwidth="4*"/>
                        <tbody>
                            <row>
<entry>uint8_t</entry><entry>
<para>address Array - this array will be populated with the I2C bus addresses found (minimum three elements) </para>
</entry>
                            </row>
                        </tbody>
                        </tgroup>
                    </table>
                    </para>
                </formalpara>
                <formalpara><title>Returns</title>

<para>0 if no i2c device is found; -1 if error is found or n &gt; 0, where n is the number of I2C bus address found </para>
</formalpara>
</para>
